# Exercism.io Exercises

Here is a collection of my programming exercises from Exercism.io, which is "an online platform designed to help you improve your coding skills through practice and mentorship."

You can learn more about it here:  https://exercism.io

I am using this tool to keep sharp on syntax for my most know languages (C/C++), and as a resource for learning new languages as well.  I find the test-driven development is great for flexing my mind muscles.
